dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation, Manasquan Inlet
dct_description_sm: This survey map depicts a sand bar that sits across the mouth of the Manasquan River as well as details about contiguous water levels. It includes a smaller inset map with the mean tide level for the Atlantic ocean.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
